snippet.title: Super Mighty Power Man - Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description: Super Mighty Power Man is a true 8-bit retro action-platformer keeping with the best 80’s and 90’s video games of the genre. A true Run n’ Gun that will ensure you hours of fun with hordes of monsters to fight, tons of traps to avoid and epic bosses to defeat!
